languages.text: "Почему? Вы чего-то стыдитесь? Меня? Не хотите, чтобы другие знали о страсти, что, подобно виноградной лозе, оплела и соединила наши сердца? По-моему, это восхитило ваших слуг".
"Why? Are you embarrassed? Embarrassed of me, perhaps? Do you wish to keep secret the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a verdant vine? I think your servants found it exciting."
languages.original_text: "Почему? Вы чего-то стыдитесь? Меня? Не хотите, чтобы другие знали о страсти, что, подобно виноградной лозе, оплела и соединила наши сердца? По-моему, это восхитило ваших слуг".

traits.locale_text: "Why? Are you ashamed of something? Ashamed of me, perhaps? Do you not want others to know about the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a vine? I think it excited your servants."

languages.text: « Pour quelle raison ? cela vous gêne ? Auriez-vous honte de MOI ? Souhaitiez-vous garder secrète la passion qui unit nos cœurs telle une vigne-vierge en plein essor ? Du reste, je crois que vos serviteurs ont trouvé nos ébats tout à fait réjouissants. »
languages.original_text: "Why? Are you embarrassed? Embarrassed of me, perhaps? Do you wish to keep secret the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a verdant vine? I think your servants found it exciting."

languages.text: “为什么？是你觉得尴尬吗？还是说，你为我感到尴尬？激情将我们的心灵紧紧缠绕在一起，就像青藤一样，将我们联结在一起。莫非你打算将这件事情保密吗？我猜，你的仆人一定认为这件事情很激动人心。”
languages.original_text: "Why? Are you embarrassed? Embarrassed of me, perhaps? Do you wish to keep secret the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a verdant vine? I think your servants found it exciting."

languages.text: "Warum? Ist es Euch peinlich? Bin ich Euch vielleicht peinlich? Möchtet Ihr die Leidenschaft geheim halten, die unsere Herzen umschlungen und vereint hat wie eine kräftige Kletterpflanze? Ich glaube, Eure Diener fanden es aufregend."
languages.original_text: "Why? Are you embarrassed? Embarrassed of me, perhaps? Do you wish to keep secret the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a verdant vine? I think your servants found it exciting."

languages.text: «¿Por qué? ¿Te da vergüenza? Es por mí, ¿verdad? ¿Quieres mantener en secreto la pasión que ha entrelazado y unido nuestros corazones como una enredadera? Creo que a tus sirvientes les ha encantado».
languages.original_text: "Why? Are you embarrassed? Embarrassed of me, perhaps? Do you wish to keep secret the passion that has entwined and united our hearts like a verdant vine? I think your servants found it exciting."

languages.text: 「なぜ？恥ずかしがっているの？それとも、あたしのことを恥だと思ってる？青々としたつるのように絡み、結びついたあたしたちの情熱を秘密にしておきたいの？あなたの従者たちは、それを刺激的だと感じていたと思うけど」

languages.text: "Neden? Utandın mı? Benden mi utandın yoksa? Taze bir asma gibi kalplerimize dolanmış, birbirine bağlamış tutkumuzu bir sır olarak mı saklamak isterdin? Bence hizmetkârların bunu heyecan verici bulmuş."
